&lt;p&gt;This in-situ leaf size data was collected during fieldwork in the Kimberley region of Western Australia in July 2021. Ten randomly selected plants were studied, and for each plant five randomly selected leaves were measured. Leaves were collected under flora licence FT61000860 and directly measured on site. The dataset contains sampling location, sampling date and leaf size measurement in cm. The same collected leaves will also be used for analysis of prey spectra.&lt;/p&gt;
