&lt;p&gt;Number of files and types: 1 table (.xlsx), 1 pdf&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keywords: Atom Probe Tomography; Nanoscale; 3D; reconstruction parameters; Minerals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is the updated August 2022 dataset version, which includes new APT reconstruction parameters of sphalerite and corundum as well as 2 jpg images of supporting information.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>

