&lt;p&gt;Special software required to open files: Excel&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Geographic information (if relevant): Western Australia&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keywords: cancer services pharmacist, cancer clinic, oral antineoplastic agent, Australia&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>

